{"id":430745,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":5,"day":18}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"213","ytitle":"","mtitle":"小钢琴手","ftitle":"","authors":["于之"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"于之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赞在“上海之春”演出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六岁儿童邵丹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比布娃娃大一点儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小苹果脸蛋红通通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教她上台要行礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她却朝钢琴鞠了个躬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大钢琴却听她指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起歌来叮叮咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四只小天鹅又歌又舞(注)，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天的音符在跳跳蹦蹦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符化为轻巧的蒲公英，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落到叔叔阿姨的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音符化作朵朵小花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浴着阳光，迎着春风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她刚从琴櫈上爬下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声的狂飚要把她卷上天空……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔吧，可爱的小天鹅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔吧，新中国幸福的儿童!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注)“四只小天鹅”，邵丹演奏节目之一。"}]}